%% ============================================================
%% Fluxo de pareamento, captura e renderizacao do sinal sEMG.
%% Referenciado em: cap-experimentos-resultados.tex (4.4.3 e 4.4.4)
%% Label: fig:IRISMobileFluxoCaptura
%% ============================================================
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as Pesquisador
    participant Tela as BluetoothScreen +<br/>CaptureScreen
    participant Ctx as BluetoothContext
    participant RN as react-native-<br/>bluetooth-classic
    participant Disp as NeuroEstimulator<br/>(ESP32 + HC-06)
    participant Acc as BinaryFrameAccumulator<br/>(utils/binaryDecoder)
    participant Hook as useStreamData<br/>(hook)
    participant Chart as SEMGChart
    participant Sess as SessionContext
    participant FS as expo-file-system

    Note over U,Tela: (i) Permissoes e listagem de pareados
    U->>Tela: Abre tela de Bluetooth
    Tela->>Ctx: requestPermissions()
    Ctx->>Ctx: PermissionsAndroid.requestMultiple<br/>(BLUETOOTH_CONNECT, BLUETOOTH_SCAN,<br/>ACCESS_FINE_LOCATION)
    Ctx->>RN: getBondedDevices()
    RN-->>Ctx: lista de pareados
    Ctx->>Ctx: filtra por nome "NeuroEstimulator"
    Ctx-->>Tela: neuraDevices[]

    Note over U,Disp: (ii) Conexao SPP
    U->>Tela: Toca em dispositivo
    Tela->>Ctx: connectBluetooth(address)
    Ctx->>RN: connectToDevice(<br/>{ secureSocket: false,<br/>connectionType: 'binary' })
    RN->>Disp: socket SPP estabelecido
    Disp-->>RN: ok
    Ctx->>RN: subscribe onDataReceived,<br/>onDeviceDisconnected

    Note over U,Chart: (iii) Captura e streaming a 215 Hz
    U->>Tela: Inicia captura
    Tela->>Ctx: startStream() + startRecording()
    Ctx->>FS: cria recording_<ts>.csv<br/>com cabecalho "timestamp,value"
    Ctx->>Disp: comando "Start Stream" (codigo 11)

    loop A cada 50 amostras (~ 232 ms)
        Disp-->>RN: quadro binario 108 B<br/>[0xAA, 0x0D, ts32 LE,<br/>cnt16 LE, 50 x int16 LE]
        RN-->>Ctx: callback onDataReceived (Base64)
        Ctx->>Acc: feed(bytes)
        Acc-->>Ctx: StreamDataPacket{ timestamp, samples[50] }
        Ctx->>Ctx: append em streamBufferRef<br/>+ csvPendingRef
    end

    loop A cada 500 ms (Hook)
        Hook->>Ctx: drena streamBufferRef
        Hook->>Hook: downsample (fator 5)<br/>+ janela de 4 s / 160 pontos
        Hook-->>Chart: setData(amostras)
        Ctx->>FS: append CSV (linha-a-linha)
    end

    Note over U,FS: (iv) Encerramento da captura
    U->>Tela: Para captura
    Tela->>Ctx: stopStream() + stopRecording()
    Ctx->>Disp: comando "Stop Stream" (codigo 12)
    Ctx->>Acc: reset()
    Ctx->>FS: flush final + close
    Ctx->>Sess: addRecording({ filePath, sampleCount,<br/>duration, sampleRate })
    Sess->>Sess: persiste em SQLite com<br/>sync_status = 'pending'

    Note over U,Disp: (v) Falha de conexao (recuperacao)
    Disp-->>RN: desconexao inesperada
    RN-->>Ctx: onDeviceDisconnected
    Ctx-->>Tela: showConnectionErrorModal = true
    Tela-->>U: alerta + opcao de reconectar
